{"tid":300033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英殖遺物變禁忌？維園女王銅像被圍封","createTime":"2017-06-27T14:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T16:03:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31f171e3f1574e6b6656fd3eab421fdc2eeb7107","tid":300033,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498560479_058d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498560479_058d.jpg&h=7cbf4114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 國家主席習近平將於周四訪港3日，警方近日已在灣仔佈防，設置大型水馬等保安措施，灣仔區議員楊雪盈今日在facebook上載一張相片，指維園內的維多利亞女王銅像外圍被封上圍板，令人質疑是為習近平到訪做準備，避免習來港時看到英殖遺物。<br />\n<br />\n有網民對圍板行動表示憤怒，有人反問中央是否「一個舊銅像也容不下？氣量少得可憐了！」，有人揶揄建議維多利亞公園亦要改名，避開英殖文化，有人甚至笑言可能名稱擁英殖特色的街道亦不可行經。<br />\n<br />\n在銅鑼灣維園的維多利亞女王銅像已有逾120年歷史，銅像去年因油漆剝落，政府曾委託承辦商復修，但復修物料太厚令銅像細節消失，銅像顏色變深，惹來批評做法不專業。<br />\n<br />\n楊雪盈回覆《蘋果》指，過去維園舉辦各類活動時，都會尊重場地設施，未見過有人做類似的改動，對今次舉動感到奇怪，「又唔見佢有咩用途，除咗要遮住（銅像）諗唔到有乜作用。」<br />\n<br />\n【網民點睇】<br />\nChun West Chu：很明顯不想俾習大大看到英殖遺物<br />\nYuki Wan：遮住女皇對眼，暗示女皇都冇眼睇？<br />\nKitty Pak：一個舊銅像也容不下？氣量少得可憐了！<br />\nRay Leung：拆左佢呀笨<br />\nKwok Lily：公園名都改埋lar <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170627/56883692\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170627%2F56883692&d=RWFR0yae4du%2Bkt%2BvTl7o6AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=4a8bfc67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170627%2F56883692&h=1c7b9778\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170627/56883692</a>"},{"pid":"9b6cef809411ac067992e4f77bcb63c84fd97051","tid":300033,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170627/large/1498560497_f8d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170627%2Flarge%2F1498560497_f8d8.jpg&h=bed8d018&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n從正面角度完全看不到維多利亞女王銅像。（楊雪盈facebook圖片）"},{"pid":"c41f0f77daa2b8b0e75f46a0adcfe020459da5d0","tid":300033,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"港英米字旗, 龍獅旗+雜種/共產黨/中國滾出香港"},{"pid":"eee8d56ab9f79a1cd43df0b2ddd95d2760e7703e","tid":300033,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"改名做雜種公園啦"},{"pid":"5492038aa17f27fe7164ecf53a2e2fa1a7e329a2","tid":300033,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:01:52.000Z","msg":"咁應該用殘體字喎&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"c36b6965903f984689876f1e3cf7a44fba72d965","tid":300033,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}